lability, the platform integrates Kubernetes-compliant operators and cloud providers while supporting reusable, organization-specific templates and enforceable policies. It empowers engineering teams to move fast without compromising on governance—turning cloud-native complexity into a manageable, traceable, and repeatable system.","devstats_url":"https://insights.linuxfoundation.org/project/opencontrolplane","lfx_slug":"opencontrolplane","oss":true,"other_links":[{"name":"Calendar","url":"https://zoom-lfx.platform.linuxfoundation.org/meetings/opencontrolplane"},{"name":"iCal","url":"https://webcal.prod.itx.linuxfoundation.org/lfx/lf0aotN8oncp0sZXSx"},{"name":"Charter","url":"https://lfx-cdn-prod.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/project-artifacts/opencp/opencp_Charter.pdf?v=1777662944841"}],"repositories":[{"url":"https://github.com/openmcp-project/metrics-operator","primary":true}]},{"category":"NeoNephos Foundation Projects","homepage_url":"https://documentation.apeirora.eu/platform-mesh","id":"neonephos-foundation-projects--all--platform-mesh","logo_url":"http://landscape.neonephos.org/logos/bc4e81dfd89e075d50cde7d939ccebb83680d8e818cf8c9ad6a1d068fde16a3a.svg","name":"Platform Mesh","subcategory":"All","accepted_at":"2025-08-29","annotations":{"project_org":"https://github.com/platform-mesh"},"crunchbase_url":"https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/neonephos","description":"Platform Mesh establishes interoperability between multiple providers by building upon the Kubernetes API and resource model. It enables a standardized concept for Services coming from Managed Service Providers through the Kubernetes API thereby  allowing developers and admins to discover, access, and order services from various sources through their beloved kubectl.","devstats_url":"https://insights.linuxfoundation.org/project/platform-mesh","lfx_slug":"platform-mesh","oss":true,"other_links":[{"name":"Calendar","url":"https://zoom-lfx.platform.linuxfoundation.org/meetings/platform-mesh"},{"name":